{
  "texts": [
    "When working with large transformer models for SML and zero-shot classification, we use the same pre-processing steps that were used during original model pre-training.",
    "In Table 1 we show combinations of methods and text representations we evaluate here.",
    "There are other possible combinations we do not survey (e.g., using dictionary output or distributed representations as input for simpler SML methods or enriching dictionaries using distributed representations).",
    "We briefly discuss several challenging decisions related to model specification and present the choices we make in our systematic evaluation.",
    "Appendix C contains more details on the technicalities of our implementations."
  ]
}